---
source: crates/duckpond/tests/parse_spec.rs
expression: spec
---
SPEC: Session expiration
  SUMMARY: Sessions expire after a period of inactivity to reduce the blast
    radius of stolen tokens.
  REQUIREMENT: Idle timeout
    The system SHALL expire authenticated sessions after 30 minutes of
      inactivity.
    SCENARIO: Idle user
      GIVENS:
        an authenticated user
      WHENS:
        the user makes no requests for 30 minutes
      THENS:
        the next request returns 401
        the session token is invalidated server-side
      MARKS: test: code
